      "utterance": "对，Etcd集群是关键判断节点。如果集群不存在或者状态异常，就需要走LoadBalancer分支去协调领域专家介入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VocabExists",
        "EngageDomainExperts",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Etcd集群的判断节点，用菱形表示。然后No分支连到LoadBalancer，Yes分支继续往下走。接下来是不是要判断IngressController的状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IsVocabFAIR",
